### **Material Information Summary**  

#### **Index Change Announcement**  
- **Infratil Limited (IFT)** will be **added to the S&P/ASX 200 Index**, effective **open of trading on 23 July 2025**.  
- **Spartan Resources Limited (SPR)** will be **removed** (due to acquisition by Ramelius Resources Limited (RMS)), **same effective date (23 July 2025)**.  

*No other material information identified.*
